# 📊 Global Socioeconomic Data Dashboard

## 🔍 Overview
This project analyzes global socioeconomic data using Power BI to uncover insights on income inequality, women's education, and migration trends.

## 🚀 Features
- Interactive dashboards
- Multi-country analysis (15+ countries)
- Data storytelling with visual insights

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Power BI
- Python (data preprocessing)
- SQL

## 📈 Key Insights
- Higher education levels correlate with lower income inequality
- Migration trends vary significantly across regions

